{"article_id":"bfMdpO2VHkmqxh3D","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The bipartisan call","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to ban or better regulate \" bump stocks \"","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"after the Las Vegas gunman appeared to use them","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to boost his arsenal ' s lethality","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"is facing some resistance from gun-rights advocates ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"even as the National Rifle Association opens the door to new rules .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"Gun Owners of America , a nonprofit lobbying group , announced its opposition Thursday to any such restrictions .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"`` Gun Owners of America opposes a ban on bump stocks , \"","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Executive Director Erich Pratt said in a statement ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"noting","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that the Obama administration ' s ATF allowed the devices","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"\" to help gun owners with disabilities fire their weapons . \"","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Pratt added ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"\" Any type of ban will be ignored by criminals","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and only serve to disarm honest citizens. \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"He said","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"it ' s \" sad to see some Republicans quickly call for a vote on gun control . \"","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"\" Bump stocks \" can be used","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"to effectively convert semi-automatic rifles","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"to fire so rapidly","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"as to simulate an automatic weapon .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"The devices were found on guns","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"used by Las Vegas shooter Stephen Paddock ,","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"who killed 59 and injured hundreds Sunday night .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"Lawmakers on both sides of the aisle have quickly moved to consider new rules and a possible ban on the devices , in a rare point of concurrence for Republicans and Democrats in the gun control debate .","depth":2},{"id":25,"text":"In a major development , the NRA called Thursday for a federal review of \" bump stocks \"","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"and suggested","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"new rules might be needed , in its first statement on the Las Vegas shooting .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"\" The NRA believes","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"that devices","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"designed","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"to allow semi-automatic rifles to function like fully-automatic rifles","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"should be subject to additional regulations , \"","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"the NRA said .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"\" In Las Vegas , reports indicate","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that certain devices were used","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"to modify the firearms","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"involved , \"","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"the NRA said .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"\" Despite the fact","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"that the Obama administration approved the sale of bump fire stocks on at least two occasions ,","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"the National Rifle Association is calling on the Bureau of Alcohol , Tobacco , Firearms and Explosives","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"( BATFE )","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"to immediately review","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"whether these devices comply with federal law . \"","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"But GOA ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"which on its website features a quote from ex-GOP Rep. Ron Paul","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"calling the group the only \" no compromise \" gun lobby ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"tweeted ,","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"\" No law","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"-- including a 'bump stock ' ban --","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"would 've stopped the Las Vegas shooting . \"","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"While some congressional Republicans are on board with a \" bump stock \" review ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"others are not .","depth":6},{